### Assign Coach - Head Coach for Swimming
POST {{host}}/api/coach-assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "9000001",
  "eventRsc": "SWMW400MFR------------",
  "function": "COACH",
  "organisation": "ESP",
  "accreditationFunction": "Coach"
}

### Assign Assistant Coach
POST {{host}}/api/coach-assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "9000002",
  "eventRsc": "SWMW400MFR------------",
  "function": "AST_COA",
  "organisation": "ESP"
}

### Get Coach Assignment by ID
GET {{host}}/api/coach-assignments/9000001_SWMW400MFR----------------------------
Accept: application/json

### List Coaches by RSC prefix (event level)
GET {{host}}/api/coach-assignments/by-rsc/SWMW400MFR
Accept: application/json

### List Coaches by RSC prefix (discipline level)
GET {{host}}/api/coach-assignments/by-rsc/SWM
Accept: application/json

### Validation: missing function
POST {{host}}/api/coach-assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "9000003",
  "eventRsc": "SWMW400MFR------------",
  "function": "",
  "organisation": "USA"
}
